Description: Punto-style ru<->en layout corrector — install and use (no Fcitx5)
 After install: log out and log in once (or reboot) so the "input" group
 membership applies. Then punto-switcher-daemon starts automatically with
 your desktop session.
 .
 No Fcitx5. Qt6 GUI: punto-switcher-config edits ~/.config/punto-switcher/daemon.ini.
 .
 Layout switching on KDE Plasma uses qdbus6 when available.
